5M_*.sub

Description:
- Building of histograms from nominal samples and samples with applied systematics
  (Samples: nominal, _JES, _etrk, _eb).
- Calculation of 1sigma histograms for each systematic (_JES, _etrk, _eb, _xsec).
- Merging of nominal histograms PTF1S_PTF2S.
- Calculation of Stat-only and Stat + Sys 95% CL limits on xsec_sig.
- Combination of 95% CL limits on xsec_sig from A and B categories (Stat-only and Stat + Sys).

