Plots:
PTF1S_PTF2S_Chi2LD.pdf : Prompt Track Fraction of leading vs subleading small jet (Low definition bins)
PTF1S_PTF2S_Chi2HD.pdf : Prompt Track Fraction of leading vs subleading small jet (High definition bins)
CombinedCLstat.pdf : Chi2 vs xsec_signal from the combination of the same graph from Prompt Track Fraction of leading vs subleading small jet (Low definition bins) in both A, B categories (Stat only)
CombinedCLstatsys.pdf : Chi2 vs xsec_signal from the combination of the same graph from Prompt Track Fraction of leading vs subleading small jet (Low definition bins) in both A, B categories (Stat+Sys)

